i%C3%AAu/author-v6D2LCbIpae0gM4Dq3ytUA">Lương Khải Siêu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Th%E1%BA%A7n-Ph%C3%B9-t%E1%BA%A1m-tr%C3%BA-th%C6%B0-ho%C3%A0i/poem-Nk_Jc1_l7vyVdFLrNVTGtg">Thần Phù tạm trú thư hoài - 神符暫住書懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-_WwJUp8k9thJYDiKeky3PA">Phạm Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-Qu%E1%BB%B3-ph%E1%BB%A7-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-k%C3%BD-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-gi%C3%A1m-L%C3%BD-t%C3%A2n-kh%C3%A1ch-nh%E1%BA%A5t-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-1aKtPZzgdx86nyA-olwbPw">Thu nhật Quỳ phủ vịnh hoài phụng ký Trịnh giám, Lý tân khách nhất bách vận - 秋日夔府詠懷奉寄鄭監李賓客一百韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/Tr%C3%B9ng-t%E1%BB%91ng/poem-GsRQ4eOWsP7kUnPRj8l7rg">Trùng tống - 重送</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Gia-K%E1%BB%B7/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-gi%E1%BA%A3i-t%E1%BB%AD-phu-th%C3%AA/poem-nvWXldPQFCgPzVvH2hpTWw">Vương giải tử phu thê - 王解子夫婦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Gia-K%E1%BB%B7/author-WRSP543j56aeSlO4dZfsBQ">Ngô Gia Kỷ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-H%C6%B0u/Xu%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%8Bch-t%E1%BB%ADu-t%E1%BB%89nh/poem-8Vu9WhjhmvkwcBu3RjspSQ">Xuân tịch tửu tỉnh - 春夕酒醒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-H%C6%B0u/author-YaU63-B8n1CAEl8OjKg7AQ">Bì Nhật Hưu</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
